name: L'HOMME YVES SAINT LAURENT ULTIME
description: His allure remains, but he is more mysterious now. He will let you into his world, but he'll keep part of it for himself. He is authentic, and his desires, carnal. He walks with a self-assuredness, in the knowledge that people are watching. His charisma is intoxicating. Wild and free, he lives intensely but never loses control. He is a vital force, connected to the world around him - but also distant, untouchable.
